
Renews afs token all 30 secods.

./aexe -t 30 -p ./.p ./sayHello.sh


Crontab file:

30,40 6 * * * /dshome/adelmann/AMAS-Doc/amas-cron-job


Add, Delete and list a crontab:

crontab ./amas-cron-job                   
crontab -r
crontab -l


